{
  "enabled": true,
  "name": "Update File Tree Documentation",
  "description": "",
  "version": "1",
  "when": {
    "type": "userTriggered",
    "patterns": [
      "src/**/*",
      "package.json",
      "tsconfig.json",
      "rollup.config.js",
      "README.md",
      ".PRODUCT/**/*",
      "public/**/*"
    ]
  },
  "then": {
    "type": "askAgent",
    "prompt": "## Prompt\nPlease update the \"File Tree Documentation.md\" file with the latest project structure:\n1. use visualisation (tree structure + emoji icons) to show the project structure\n2. use emoji icons to differentiate between folders 📁 and files \n3. add usage descriptions for files and folders\n4. add descriptions for folders only for non-core content\n5. documents contain only tree structures and usage descriptions\n6. Translate sage descriptions into Chinese\n\n\n## Reference tree structure\n```\n./space-fill/\n├── 📄 **.md                # **\n├── 📄 **.md                # **\n│\n├── 📁 **/                  # **\n│   ├── 📄 **.js            # **\n│   ├── 📄 **.html          # **\n│   └── 📄 **.json          # **\n│\n└── 📁 **/                  # **\n    ├── 📄 **.ts            # **\n    │\n    └── 📁 **/              # **\n        └── 📁 **/          # **\n            └── 📄 **.md    # **\n```"
  }
}